item.title: CVE-2019-6526|2024-08-04T20:23:21.401Z -- moxa -- iks%2C%20eds
item.description: Moxa IKS-G6824A series Versions 4.5 and prior, EDS-405A series Version 3.8 and prior, EDS-408A series Version 3.8 and prior, and EDS-510A series Version 3.8 and prior use plaintext transmission of sensitive data, which may allow an attacker to capture sensitive data such as an administrative password.
